Limber Framework is a MVC PHP Framework build on top of PHP 5.3

The real code of Framework is splitted into the following layers:

https://github.com/wilkerlucio/limber-support - General and core PHP support code
https://github.com/wilkerlucio/limber-record - Database Abstraction
https://github.com/wilkerlucio/limber-pack - Controllers and Views
https://github.com/wilkerlucio/limber-spec - BDD Development

This repository will make the integration between the layers above.

NOTE: the old content of this repository was moved to limber-support repository, in the future this repository will contain to code to integrate the limber layers.